                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10021" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0342</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">316 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从东方智慧到全球基因：中信戴卡企业文化何以在墨西哥工厂落地生花？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From Eastern Wisdom to Global DNA: How CITIC Dicastal&#39;s Corporate Culture Came to Life in its Mexican Factories？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘海鸥，王梦泽，王海英，苏国尘</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">燕山大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中信戴卡股份有限公司墨西哥工厂</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">党群部门/思想政治工作部门/企业文化部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业文化；跨文化管理；中信戴卡；戴卡墨西哥工厂；2025百优案例；国企专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CITIC Corporate Culture; Cross-cultural Management; Dicastal; Dicastal Mexico </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在“一带一路”倡议纵深推进的时代背景下，企业文化作为人文交流与价值传递的重要载体，其“走出去”不仅是中国企业国际化的必修课，更是推动“一带一路”从基础设施“硬联通”向文明互鉴“软联通”升级的关键路径。案例系统解构中信戴卡以“仁义礼智信”为核心的企业文化在墨西哥工厂的跨文化实践。在中墨文化价值差异、管理范式分歧与创新理念冲突的复杂语境下，企业以 “仁”凝聚人心、以“义”规范准则、以“礼”弥合差异、以“智”革新机制、以“信”筑牢根基，通过五位一体的跨文化管理策略推动深度融合，最终实现企业发展效能与本土社会认同的双向跃升，为中国企业全球化发展提供文化融合的实践样本。案例旨在帮助学生理解中国企业中华优秀传统文化融入企业文化出海实践，认识传统文化浸润形成的企业软实力在国际竞争中的关键作用，激发学生以中华优秀传统文化为根基的文化自信，推动中国企业参与全球规则制定的责任感。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the context of the deepening of the “Belt and Road” initiative, corporate culture, as an important carrier of humanistic exchanges and value transfer, is not only a necessary course for Chinese enterprises to internationalize, but also a key factor in promoting the “Belt and Road” initiative. It is also a key path to promote the upgrading of the “Belt and Road” from the “hard connectivity” of infrastructure to the “soft connectivity” of mutual understanding of civilizations. This case systematically deconstructs the cross-cultural practice of CITIC Dicastal&#39;s corporate culture of “benevolence, righteousness, propriety, wisdom and trust” in the Mexican factory. In the complex context of cultural value differences between China and Mexico, management paradigm differences and innovation concept conflicts, the company uses “benevolence” to unite people&#39;s hearts, “righteousness” to standardize norms, “propriety” to bridge differences In the complex context of “benevolence” to unite people, “righteousness” to regulate norms, “propriety” to bridge differences, “wisdom” to innovate mechanisms, and “trust” to build a solid foundation, the company promotes in-depth integration through the five-in-one cross-cultural management strategy, and ultimately realizes a two-way leap in the effectiveness of the company&#39;s development and local social acceptance, and provides a practical example of cultural integration for the globalization development of Chinese enterprises. The case is designed to help students understand the development of Chinese enterprises in globalization. This case aims to help students understand the integration of Chinese outstanding traditional culture into the corporate culture of Chinese enterprises in the practice of going overseas, recognize the key role of the soft power of enterprises formed by the infiltration of traditional culture in international competition, inspire students to take Chinese outstanding traditional culture as the foundation of cultural self-confidence, and promote the sense of responsibility of Chinese enterprises to participate in the formulation of global rules.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业文化》、《跨文化管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">跨文化管理与企业文化落地；跨文化管理的文化层次；跨文化管理的文化冲突；跨文化管理的文化策略；跨文化管理的文化作用</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
